---
name: e2e-streaming
description: E2E test for streaming chat completion
model:
  id: gpt-4o
  provider: openai
  apiType: chat
  connection:
    kind: reference
    name: mock-openai
  options:
    temperature: 0.7
    additionalProperties:
      stream: true
inputs:
  - name: topic
    kind: string
    default: TypeScript
template:
  format:
    kind: nunjucks
  parser:
    kind: prompty
---
system:
You are a helpful assistant.

user:
Tell me about {{topic}}.
